WHY THESE RESTRICTIONS:
To ensure stability and prevent conflicts, this framework maintains a single
canonical version. Allowing redistribution could lead to version fragmentation
where multiple incompatible copies exist in the ecosystem, causing conflicts
and compatibility issues (similar to "DLL hell"). By maintaining one official
distribution channel, all users benefit from the same stable, tested version.

DEVELOPMENT PREVIEW NOTICE:
This software is currently in active development and is not yet ready for
public release. The license terms may change when the software reaches a
stable release version.

